@startuml
title Sequence: Update Customer

actor Client
Client -> CustomerController: PUT /api/customers/{id}
CustomerController -> CustomerService: update(id, customer)
CustomerService -> CustomerRepository: findById(id)
CustomerRepository --> CustomerService: customerFound
CustomerService -> CustomerRepository: save(updatedCustomer)
CustomerRepository --> CustomerService: updatedCustomer
CustomerService --> CustomerController: updatedCustomer
CustomerController --> Client: 200 OK + updated JSON
@enduml